title: Oct. 15-16 prep football schedule
text:
THURSDAY
7 p.m. — Millington vs. East at Melrose, Sheffield vs. Hamilton at Crump, MLK Prep vs. Hillcrest at Whitehaven, Oakhaven vs. Mitchell at J.P. Freeman, Munford vs. Overton at Southwind, Kingsbury vs. Ridgeway at Halle, Douglass vs. Trezevant at Fairgrounds.
FRIDAY
7 p.m. — Melrose at Bolivar Central, MUS at Briarcrest, Washington vs. Carver at Crump, St. Benedict at Christian Brothers, Lewisburg at Clarksdale-Miss., Hernando at DeSoto Central, USJ at Fayette Aca., Covington at Fayette-Ware, Northpoint at Harding, Olive Branch at Horn Lake, West Memphis at Jonesboro-Ark., Bolton at Kirby, ECS at Lausanne, Westwood at Lexington Catholic, Northside vs. Middle College at Melrose, KIPP at Middleton, Marion at Mountain Home-Ark., Center Hill at Saltillo-Miss., Columbus-Miss. at Southaven, Central at Southwind, St. George's at Tipton-Rosemark Aca., Tunica Institute at West Memphis Christian, Lake Cormorant at West Point-Miss., Brighton vs. Wooddale at Halle.
